Unitron:



Unitron flipped over Hot Rod's back, and landed on one hand and one knee.  
"Ha.  Ultra Magnus, an idiot.  Kup, a weakling with no leadership ability.  
Ha, all pathetic.  You were just last one left standing.  In fact, the Matrix 
didn't even pick you now that my thoughts flow more clearly.  You only stole 
it from Galvatron.  And even then, when you were Rodimus Prime, you had the 
chance to defeat the Decepticons numerous time, but kept losing.  How 
pathetic."

Unitron leapt forward, sending a foot flinging out towards Hot Rod's face in 
a jump kick.
